## BACKEND TODO APP

### GET: Obtener todas las tareas
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### POST: Crear una nueva tarea
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Nueva Tarea 2",
  "description": "Descripción de la tarea 2"
}

###

### PUT: Actualizar una tarea por su ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/6749591491310a9df03501f0 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Tarea actualizada",
  "description": "Nueva descripción"
}

###

### PUT: Cambiar el estado de una tarea por su ID
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/6749591491310a9df03501f0 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### DELETE: Eliminar una tarea por su ID
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/63f8e8b2c6f8a1283f7e0f9a HTTP/1.1
Accept: application/json

